  "keyFeatures": [
    "Random animal image endpoints for cats, floppa, capybara, hyrax, manul, and rabbits",
    "PocketBase integration for remote image storage with automatic view tracking",
    "Local filesystem image serving via LocalAnimal for self-hosted collections",
    "Built-in PocketBase admin proxy with token-based authentication",
    "Svelte frontend with admin panel for managing animal collections",
    "Docker-based deployment with multi-stage builds",
    "CORS-enabled API for cross-origin browser access",
    "iOS Shortcuts support via VIM ID-filtered macka endpoint"
